<div
  class="relative mx-auto mb-16 mt-4 flex max-w-[600px] flex-col gap-1 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-b from-[#260F56] to-[#4D2E91] p-5 font-zeitung"
>
  <h2 class="text-shadow-pink m-0 font-zeitung text-xl not-italic">
    # Our mission
  </h2>
  <p class="text-fujo-green">
    > Empowering fujoshi and other online subcultures to shape their web through
